"65:9:1" : {s: 65, a: 9, w: 1, r: "ذوق", t: "فَذَاقَتْ", l: "ذَاقُ", lc: 36, tl: "fadhāqat", lb: "আস্বাদন করা, স্বাদ গ্রহণ করা",e: "So it tasted", b: "স্বাদ নিয়েছে অতঃপর", i: "maka mereka merasakan", f: 1, rm: "to taste/experience/try/perceive. One who tastes, cause to taste.", ag: "فاء عطف وفعل ماض ", eg: "Conjunctive fa and Verb Perfect ", tag: "V", pos: "V", att: "PERF", qual: "", deg: "3", gen: "F", num: "S", mood: "", lu: "ذَآئِقَةُ"},
