"65:10:6" : {s: 65, a: 10, w: 6, r: "وقي", t: "فَٱتَّقُوا۟", l: "ٱتَّقَىٰ", lc: 166, tl: "fa-ittaqū", lb: "কোনো কিছুর ব্যাপারে অত্যন্ত সচেতন থাকা, আল্লাহর প্রতি সচেতন থাকা",e: "So fear", b: "অতএব তোমরা ভয় কর", i: "maka bertakwalah", f: 17, rm: "to protect, save, preserve, ward off, guard against evil and calamity, be secure, take as a shield, regard the duty. muttaqii - one who guard against evil and against that which harms and injures and is regardful of his duty towards human beings and God.", ag: "فاء استئنافية وفعل أمر صيغة ٨ وضمير متصل ", eg: "Resumption fa and Verb Imperative 8th form and Pronoun suffix ", tag: "V", pos: "V", att: "IMPV", qual: "(VIII)", deg: "2", gen: "M", num: "P", mood: "", lu: "ٱتَّقَىٰ"},
